name: Spaceworthy
description:
This is a test to see if you're spaceworthy. Fly around taking down enemies, and see if you can kill a planet! Then, see if you can do it on hardcore mode! Good luck!

Features

  • Finest 2-day quality craftsmanship
  • Space
  • Space ships
  • parallax scrolling
  • 2 whole enemy types
  • a boss
  • one planet
  • did i mention space

This was a game I made in 2 days. It took about 18 1/2 hours to do. Temper your expectations.
